Grand Architecture Changes
==

Truly asynchronous Flickr API.  Maybe using XML-RPC and Twisted.

Callback-based authentication so the calling application can handle the user interaction.


Missing Features
==

Add an loading progress bar

Upload progress bar needs work:
- Cancel
- A real progress bar instead of activity

Let user add photos to sets and groups

Set privacy options

When dropping image data store the data not a pixbuf in the model to allow
dragging of lossy data

Show date/time taken
